sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Domain as DichVuNguon
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant NotiSvc as NotificationService
participant NotiDb as Mongo_Notification
participant Realtime as SocketService
participant Client as UngDungWeb

Note over Domain,Client: Chặng 1 - Tạo thông báo và hiển thị realtime
Domain->>Gateway: POST /api/notifications (internal token)
Gateway->>NotiSvc: Forward
NotiSvc->>NotiDb: Insert notification
NotiSvc->>Realtime: Emit notification:new
NotiSvc-->>Domain: 201
User->>Client: Mở chuông thông báo
Client->>Gateway: GET /api/notifications
Gateway->>NotiSvc: Query theo user
NotiSvc-->>Client: Danh sách thông báo
